        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "So the game industry has gotten to the point where we are remaking already existing remakes, huh? ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Tactics Ogre: Reborn",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a remake of ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Tactics Ogre: Let Us Cling Together",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " for the PlayStation Portable, which is a remake of the Super Famicom strategy RPG game of the same name. The game follows Denam Powell, his sister Catiua and their friend Vyce as they are thrust into the middle of a civil war over the Valerian Isles. They will learn that life on the battlefield changes people; will you forsake your morals or will you do what is necessary to win this war?",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iVNyoeik0ig",
        "html": "<iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/iVNyoeik0ig?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"Tactics Ogre: Reborn | Story Trailer\"></iframe>",
        "metadata": {
          "title": "Tactics Ogre: Reborn | Story Trailer",
          "author_name": "Square Enix",
          "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/c/squareenixna",
          "height": 113,
          "width": 200,
          "version": "1.0",
          "provider_name": "YouTube",
          "provider_url": "https://www.youtube.com/",
          "thumbnail_height": 360,
