            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a fantastic addition to any tactical RPG fan’s library but if you’re like me and missed out on playing the original back in the day, it may feel a little lacking. If that doesn’t bother you and you just want more of what you’ve already got, then you can’t go wrong with picking this up.",
